If you look at the documentation of PDFReader, you can create a PDF using data, and display it with a PDFViewController:

```swift
guard let data = data else { return }

let document = PDFDocument(fileData: data, fileName: &quot;Sample PDF&quot;)!
//Display a PDFDocument
let readerController = PDFViewController.createNew(with: document)
navigationController?.pushViewController(readerController, animated: true)
```

or with [PDFKit][1] from Apple:

```swift
guard let data = data else, let doc = PDFDocument(data: data) { return }

let pdfView = PDFView()
pdfView.document = doc
/* present the View */
```


  [1]: https://developer.apple.com/documentation/pdfkit

